Congratulations to all winners! ğŸ‰ 
Well deserved ğŸ‘ and a big shoutout to @CrowdHackio for hosting the HackOnXDC Hackathon! 

ğŸš€ Letâ€™s #BuildOnXDC  #XDC @XinFin_Official @CrowdHackio

We are very excited to announce the winners of our 1st HackOnXDC hackathon event.  We appreciate all Teams for coming out to #hack and hope to see all of your projects launch on the #XDCNetwork.  

A strong handshake goes out to @GDCE_Official and @CrowdHackio for all their support and always @XinFin_Official for supporting this and so many other hackathons to increase the development of dApps on the XDC Network.  

WINNERS: Trade Sync- Mobile SDK- TokenX

1st Place:  Trade Sync -  An enterprise solution for trade finance.  Creating efficiencies for exporters using DLT, AI, Hyper-Productive flows, building counter party registries with deep provenance and composable tokenization to keep the integrity at each layer while transferring the ownership.  For MSME's, this technology opens up many negotiable instruments and broader financial access. 

2nd Place:  Mobile SDK - Simplifying Web2--> Web3 adoption.  This SDK eliminates all the complexities that users are going through at the moment with the wallet (Metamask, XDCPay, etc). User has to remember the seed phrase and when they using any application, they must sign a transaction, the application has to give control to another app to do the same.  With this SDK we are eliminating these steps and the user would be able to sign and verify, send, etc in the same application.

3rd Place:  TokenX -  We offer an interactive no-code platform that allows users to create a NFT collection. We provide a simple interface to airdrop NFT's just by giving JSON of addresses.  User can also share the claimable link to mint NFT at the userâ€™s convenience. We also provide dev tooling to airdrop created NFTs in batch through ready-to-use API. There are lots of actual use cases for communities, DAOs and institutions.  

Honorable Mention:  Outre Finance - Users are able to create loan offers and requests to borrow or lend to one another on their own terms.  68% of loans in the alternative lending market in Africa are P2P loans. With Outre P2P users are able to offer or request loans from each other at their own terms. Outre Finance helps with monitoring the Credit scores of users and only recommending matches to users in order to minimize the risk of default among users. This feature is very useful for those who survive on day loans to run small businesses for purposes such as inventory purchases. This product greatly reduces the cost of loans as it democratizes lending and also opens other earning avenues for users through interest.

Keep your eyes open for all the up and coming dApps building on the XDC Network. The Future is bright!

RT @invest_answers: To the Esteemed Unions and Government of Sweden,

I am writing to express my deep concern regarding the ongoing efforts to pressure #Tesla into unionizing its workforce in Sweden. While I understand the importance of unions and their role in protecting the rights of workers, I believe that the current approach being taken is misguided and could have detrimental consequences for both Tesla and Sweden as a whole.

Tesla, as a global company with a strong reputation for innovation and efficiency, has built its success on a foundation of non-unionized labor. This model has allowed the company to remain nimble, adaptable, and competitive in a rapidly changing industry. Demanding that Tesla abandon this model in favor of unionized labor would represent a significant departure from the company's core principles and could undermine its ability to thrive in the global marketplace.

Moreover, setting a precedent of forcing foreign companies to adopt Swedish union practices could have a chilling effect on future investment in Sweden. Businesses, both domestic and international, may become hesitant to establish operations in a country where labor relations are unpredictable and subject to arbitrary demands. This could lead to a decline in economic activity and job opportunities for Swedish workers.

In addition to these economic concerns, the current unionization efforts could also accelerate the development of automated technologies that could replace human workers. As unions push for higher wages and stricter working conditions, companies will be increasingly motivated to seek alternatives that are more cost-effective and less susceptible to unionization. This could lead to a significant loss of jobs in the automotive industry and other sectors that rely on human labor.

I urge the unions and the government of Sweden to tread very carefully in their dealings with Tesla. While the protection of workers' rights is undoubtedly important, it must not come at the expense of Sweden's economic competitiveness and its ability to attract foreign investment. A more constructive approach would be to engage in dialogue with Tesla to find common ground and solutions that benefit both the company and its employees.

Thank you for your time and consideration.

Sincerely, james 
cc @elonmusk

RT @S4mmyEth: Disney is coming to Web3.

Dapper Labs is partnering with the $159B entertainment conglomerate to bring Web3 IP to the masses.

Do you think the Simpsons NFT episode timing was a coincidence?

Disney acquired 21st Century Fox in 2019 which had the rights to the Simpsons.

Here's the TLDR:

- Disney is launching an NFT collectibles platform named Disney Pinnacle, in collaboration with Dapper Labs, the creator of NBA Top Shot.

- The platform is inspired by the physical pins sold at Disney theme parks, offering digital pin-inspired collectibles minted as NFTs on the Flow blockchain.

- Disney Pinnacle will feature digital pins based on characters and properties from Disney, Pixar, and Star Wars, including notable characters like Buzz Lightyear, Woody, Disney Princesses, and Darth Vader.

- Marvel, another Disney-owned IP, was not mentioned for inclusion at the platform's launch.

- Disney Pinnacle is specifically designed for mobile use, providing enhanced features and an updated economy design aimed at balancing accessibility for everyday fans and exclusive assets for collectors.

- The platform has opened its waitlist and plans to gradually onboard users for beta testing, with no specific timeline for a full public launch yet.

- Ridhima Kahn, Dapper's VP of business development and partnerships, facilitated the collaboration between Disney and Dapper Labs.

- Dapper Labs, known for its success with NBA Top Shot, developed the Flow blockchain for broader-scale consumer applications like collectibles platforms and games.

- The announcement of Disney Pinnacle aligns with recent signs of a revival in the NFT market, suggesting an upcoming wave of higher quality and more user-friendly NFT platforms and applications.

Buckle up - It's about to get wild.
